base_token_id.desc: The main lending token used for deposits and borrowing (0 for ALGO)

lst_token_id.desc: LST (Liquidity Staking Token) representing depositor shares in the pool

circulating_lst.desc: Total LST tokens currently in circulation (represents depositor claims)

total_deposits.desc: Total underlying assets deposited in the protocol

admin_account.desc: Administrative account with privileged access to protocol functions

oracle_app.desc: External oracle application for asset price feeds

ltv_bps.desc: Loan-to-Value ratio (e.g., 7500 = 75% max borrowing against collateral)

liq_threshold_bps.desc: Liquidation threshold (e.g., 8500 = 85% - liquidate when CR falls below)

interest_bps.desc: Annual interest rate charged to borrowers (e.g., 500 = 5% APR)

origination_fee_bps.desc: One-time fee charged on loan origination (e.g., 100 = 1%)

depositor_share_bps.desc: Depositors' share of interest income (calculated as 10000 - protocol_share)

active_loan_records.desc: Total number of active loans in the system

accepted_collaterals_count.desc: Count of different collateral types accepted by the protocol

last_max_borrow.desc: Last calculated maximum borrowable amount in USD (for debugging)

last_requested_loan.desc: Last requested loan amount in USD (for debugging)

debug_diff.desc: Difference between max borrow and requested (for debugging)

accepted_collaterals.desc: Registry of accepted collateral assets with their metadata

loan_record.desc: Individual borrower loan records with collateral and debt details
